minimalexample-changecontentmodel-cache-: Note shown on [[Special:ChangeContentModel]] about outdated versions of {{PAGECONTENTMODEL:}}.
doesuserexist-username-input: Label for the username field on [[Special:DoesUserExist]]
doesuserexist-perform-check: Label for the submission button on [[Special:DoesUserExist]]
doesuserexist-does-not-exist:
Message shown when no user exists with the given name.

Parameters:
* $1 - the requested name
doesuserexist-exists-exact:
Message shown when a user exists with exactly the given name.

Parameters:
* $1 - the requested name
doesuserexist-exists-normalized:
Message shown when a user exists with the normalized form of the given name.

Parameters:
* $1 - the normalized name
* $2 - the requested name
doesuserexist-exists-hidden: Message shown to privileged users when a user exists but is hidden.
